service.name: Foster Child Health Care Card
service.description: The Foster Child Health Care Card (FST HCC) is issued to the foster carer but only the foster child is named on and covered by the card. It enables foster carers to purchase Pharmaceutical Benefit Scheme (PBS) medications at reduced costs for foster children and may entitle them to concessions offered by State or Territory organisations for the foster children.
